      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely heartbroken to be parting with my pride and joy, but it's time for someone else to enjoy this beauty! Honestly, this car is in pristine condition\u2014it still has that new-car smell and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garaged and spotless. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home! You really have to see it in person to see how perfect it is. Feel free to shoot me a message!",
