    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring a 11.5:1 compression ratio and individual throttle bodies, mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. Mechanically superlative, the dual-VANOS system has been bulletproofed with Beisan seals and an upgraded oil pump disk. The rear subframe\u2014a known structural weak point\u2014has been proactively reinforced with epoxy-injected plates to ensure chassis rigidity. The factory variable M differential lock operates silently, and the suspension geometry remains true with fresh OEM bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers. This is a turn-key, concours-level driver with zero deferred maintenance and a pristine undercarriage.",
